{"subscription":{"$wrap":"$oid","v":13},"link":"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/Blogcoward/~3/cun-TsSgx-0/Glimpse-AspNet-1-3-1-Installation-Errors.aspx","title":"Glimpse AspNet 1.3.1 Installation Errors","published":{"$wrap":"$date","v":1374693644000,"h":"2013-07-24T19:20:44.000Z"},"starred":false,"read":true,"content":"<p>Given how nifty Glimpse seemed in the three minutes I spent working with it on a personal MVC app, I tried to install it locally on a work project.</p><p>No worky.</p><p>Errors in web.config, such as:</p><p><a href=\"http://www.blogcoward.com/images/www_blogcoward_com/Windows-Live-Writer/Glimpse-AspNet-1.3.1-Installation-Errors_C8AC/clip_image001_2.jpg\"><img title=\"clip_image001\" style=\"display: inline; background-image: none;\" border=\"0\" alt=\"clip_image001\" src=\"http://www.blogcoward.com/images/www_blogcoward_com/Windows-Live-Writer/Glimpse-AspNet-1.3.1-Installation-Errors_C8AC/clip_image001_thumb.jpg\" width=\"644\" height=\"368\" /></a></p><p>A bunch of errors with extra&lt;HttpModules&gt; section being added (and the like).  All of these were fixable with some manually typing.</p><p></p><p>The readme page itself threw some odd errors:</p><p><a href=\"http://www.blogcoward.com/images/www_blogcoward_com/Windows-Live-Writer/Glimpse-AspNet-1.3.1-Installation-Errors_C8AC/clip_image002_2.jpg\"><img title=\"clip_image002\" style=\"display: inline; background-image: none;\" border=\"0\" alt=\"clip_image002\" src=\"http://www.blogcoward.com/images/www_blogcoward_com/Windows-Live-Writer/Glimpse-AspNet-1.3.1-Installation-Errors_C8AC/clip_image002_thumb.jpg\" width=\"644\" height=\"415\" /></a></p><p>Those are just annoying.</p><p>The biggest issue was that every single page hit would throw some Javascript error, most of them in glimpse.pubsub, and no information would be available in Glimpse at all.</p><p><a href=\"http://www.blogcoward.com/images/www_blogcoward_com/Windows-Live-Writer/Glimpse-AspNet-1.3.1-Installation-Errors_C8AC/image_2.png\"><img title=\"image\" style=\"display: inline; background-image: none;\" border=\"0\" alt=\"image\" src=\"http://www.blogcoward.com/images/www_blogcoward_com/Windows-Live-Writer/Glimpse-AspNet-1.3.1-Installation-Errors_C8AC/image_thumb.png\" width=\"644\" height=\"312\" /></a></p><p></p><p>Tried installing through the package manager, and also tried through the console.  Upgraded the core to Glimpse 1.5.0, still no luck.</p><p><em>uninstall-package Glimpse.AspNet</em></p><p>Too bad.</p><img src=\"http://www.blogcoward.com/aggbug/932.aspx\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" /><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/Blogcoward/~4/cun-TsSgx-0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>","author":"jdn","_id":{"$wrap":"$oid","v":128}}
