the Windows 8.1 update, focusing specifically on users who use desktop machines.</li><li><a href=\"http://www.daedtech.com/throw-out-your-code\">Throw Out Your Code</a> -  Erik Dietrich discusses ‘The Endowment Effect’ and looks at how it relates to the code we developers produce, and urges us to sometimes throw that code away and start clean.</li><li><a href=\"http://visualstudiomagazine.com/articles/2013/07/15/whats-new-in-typescript-0_9.aspx\">What’s New in TypeScript 0.9</a> - Peter Vogel explores the improvements in TypeScript 0.9 in his Visual Studio Magazine article</li></ul><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/ReflectivePerspective/~4/HO2a1Ac2CaM\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>","author":"Chris Alcock","_id":{"$wrap":"$oid","v":365}}
