{"subscription":{"$wrap":"$oid","v":32},"link":"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/LosTechies/~3/Z3kfi-b-uxU/","title":"Let Me Teach You Arduino, With JavaScript!","published":{"$wrap":"$date","v":1375215373000,"h":"2013-07-30T20:16:13.000Z"},"starred":false,"read":true,"content":"Ever wanted an excuse to learn Arduino, but don’t want to learn C/C++? Don’t worry. I’ve got you covered.  I’ve published three articles on the Safari Books Online blog that show you how to take your existing JavaScript skillz and …<a href=\"http://lostechies.com/derickbailey/2013/07/30/let-me-teach-you-arduino-with-javascript/\">Continue reading <span class=\"meta-nav\">→</span></a><div class=\"feedflare\"><a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/LosTechies?a=Z3kfi-b-uxU:ybEm8brtRq0:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/LosTechies?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\"></img></a><a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/LosTechies?a=Z3kfi-b-uxU:ybEm8brtRq0:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/LosTechies?i=Z3kfi-b-uxU:ybEm8brtRq0:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a><a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/LosTechies?a=Z3kfi-b-uxU:ybEm8brtRq0:7Q72WNTAKBA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/LosTechies?d=7Q72WNTAKBA\" border=\"0\"></img></a><a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/LosTechies?a=Z3kfi-b-uxU:ybEm8brtRq0:D7DqB2pKExk\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/LosTechies?i=Z3kfi-b-uxU:ybEm8brtRq0:D7DqB2pKExk\" border=\"0\"></img></a></div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/LosTechies/~4/Z3kfi-b-uxU\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>","author":"Derick Bailey","_id":{"$wrap":"$oid","v":1692}}
