{"subscription":{"$wrap":"$oid","v":2},"link":"http://www.dotnetrocks.com/default.aspx?ShowNum=894","title":"Working with Creatives and Fabio Matsui","published":{"$wrap":"$date","v":1375329600000,"h":"2013-08-01T04:00:00.000Z"},"starred":false,"read":true,"content":"Carl and Richard talk to Fabio Matsui about working effectively with creative personnel in an organization. The conversation starts out just defining what we mean by design - the different types of designers (UX, visual, motion, graphics, etc) and their role in the team. Fabio then dives into the challenges of putting different mindsets together to create synergy - where the result is greater than the sum of its parts. Great teams make it possible to do amazing things!","author":false,"_id":{"$wrap":"$oid","v":1970}}
